This directory should contain the following items:

- idat/ directory
  contains raw illumina .idat files
  obtained from:  https://www.ega-archive.org/datasets/EGAD00010000850
  located under:  1052 Files (8.5 Gb)
  exact address:  Needs an account and access request

- samplekey.txt file
  contains meta information about samples
  obtained from:  authors of the original dataset
  located under:  provided in this repository
  exact address:  data/blueprint/input/samplekey.txt

- HM450.hg38.mask.tsv file
  contains masking information for illumina array probes
  obtained from:  https://zwdzwd.github.io/InfiniumAnnotation
  located under:  Mask information > Previous Versions > HM450
  exact address:  https://github.com/zhou-lab/InfiniumAnnotationV1/raw/main/Anno/HM450/archive/202209/HM450.hg38.mask.tsv.gz
